schichtswissenschaft in der Vergangenheit, Gegenwart und Zukunft interessieren." Mills Kelly, Assoziierter Direktor des Center for History and New Media an der George Mason University  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 4aDigitalisierung. 4aGeschichte schreiben. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Geschichte 2005-2012z9783110346787oZDB-23-OGS0 cprintz978348670704540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978348671233940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486712339423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783486712339.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-OGSc2005d2012